data.description: Gorgeous mountain views and nearby wilderness area showcase this beautiful 3-Bedroom, 3-bath home * 2.35 Acres with electrical power * Relax in your own Jacuzzi spa on private back patio * 10x19 covered patio includes BBQ and evaporative cooler * Home features newer flooring, paint, roof and kitchen appliances * fully enclosed 50x10 porch exits to covered patio, garage and an extra room that could be used as a fourth bedroom, den / office or craft room * spacious garage has a workbench, extra shelving, a 3/4 bath and two 2500-gallon water tanks. * Indoor laundry room electric washer / dryer * Includes Generac Quiet Source 18 KW generator has an AGS system * property has full snake-proof fencing and a security gate at entrance * Buyer may be able to assume existing 3.25% FHA loan. * Note: Lender pre-qual or proof of funds needed prior to making appointment.
